###Git commands
| Operation             | Commands                            |
| --------------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| Global config         | `git config --global…`              |
| Init repo             | `git init`                          |
| Add files             | `git add .`                         |
| Commit                | `git commit -m`                     |
| Create main           | `git branch -M main`                |
| Add remote            | `git remote add origin <url>`       |
| Push                  | `git push -u origin main`           |
| Pull                  | `git pull` / `git pull --rebase`    |
| Fetch                 | `git fetch origin`                  |
| Checkout branch       | `git checkout <branch>`             |
| Create branch         | `git checkout -b <branch>`          |
| Merge / Rebase        | `git merge` / `git rebase`          |
| Stash                 | `git stash`, `git stash pop`        |
| Delete remote branch  | `git push origin --delete <branch>` |
| Remove sensitive file | `git rm --cached`                   |
| Rewrite history       | `git filter-branch …`               |


###Docker 
docker pull ubuntu
docker run -it --name myubuntu -p 3000:80 ubuntu
apt-get update
apt-get install nginx -y
cd /var/www/html
nano index.html
service nginx start


docker run -it ubuntu
docker commit <container-id> myimage
docker build -t myimage .
docker images
docker-compose up -d
docker-compose down
docker compose up --build

| Purpose                  | Command                                            |
| ------------------------ | -------------------------------------------------- |
| Pull image               | `docker pull ubuntu`                               |
| Run container            | `docker run -it --name myubuntu -p 3000:80 ubuntu` |
| Install inside container | `apt-get update`, `apt-get install nginx -y`       |
| Start service            | `service nginx start`                              |
| Edit HTML                | `nano index.html`                                  |
| Commit container → image | `docker commit <container-id> myimage`             |
| Build image              | `docker build -t myimage .`                        |
| List images              | `docker images`                                    |
| Start Docker Compose     | `docker-compose up -d`                             |
| Stop Docker Compose      | `docker-compose down`                              |
| Build & run compose      | `docker compose up --build`                        |
| Install Docker (EC2)     | `sudo apt-get install docker.io`                   |
| Build image (EC2)        | `sudo docker build -t img1 .`                      |
| Run container (EC2)      | `sudo docker run -d -p 8081:8080 img1`             |
| List containers          | `sudo docker ps`                                   |
| List images              | `sudo docker images`                               |




###For nagios
docker pull jasonrivers/nagios:latest
docker run --name nagiosdemo -p 8888:80 jasonrivers/nagios:latest
Username: nagiosadmin
Password: nagios

###For AWS
[FROM ngnix:alpine
COPY . /usr/share/ngnix/html]
sudo docker build -t myapp .
sudo docker run –d –p 80:80 myapp

###For minikube
minikube start
kubectl create deployment mynginx --image=nginx
kubectl set image deployment/mynginx nginx=nginx:latest
kubectl get deployments
kubectl get pods
kubectl describe pods
kubectl expose deployment mynginx --type=NodePort --port=80 --target-port=80
kubectl get service mynginx
kubectl scale deployment mynginx --replicas=4
kubectl get pods
kubectl port-forward svc/mynginx 8081:80
kubectl delete deployment mynginx
kubectl delete service mynginx
